ink1">“虚拟人才学院”</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>报名时间：5月30日（星期四）-6月24日（星期一）12:00</p><p>运营 VTuber 团体“ <a href="https://twitter.com/nijisanji_app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a> ”的<a href="https://www.anycolor.co.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd.</a>已开始为人才发展项目“ <a href="https://vta.anycolor.co.jp/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Virtual Talent Academy (VTA)</a> ”招募新试镜。此次还将举办双人试镜。</p><p> VTA 是 ANYCOLOR 利用其过去的发行知识来开发充当虚拟肝脏 (VTuber) 的主播的计划。到目前为止，Nijisanji 已经推出了 10 多个肝脏，包括毛茛属和 VOLTACTION。</p><p>此次，除了现有的VTA海选之外，还将举行双人海选。添加了附加条件，包括配对申请人关系密切。</p><p><a href="https://vta.anycolor.co.jp/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000909.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link2">《RK音乐》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.virhx8uxyj3g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2